text:
Aroma: nice hoppy grapefruit/pine cone smell, combined with blackcurrent smell and flavour, blackcurrent cake, some apricot ;
Appearance: reddish black, opaque, big tan head (moderately persisting) ;
Taste: a bit acidic, low to medium bitterness, low sweetness ;
Palate: creamy, moderately low carbonation, low alcoholic feel, medium full body, moderately persisting background bitterness.
Kinda good, but not my prefered style.
